                    <span class="arrow">&#10230;</span>
                </div>
                <div class="custom-card col-xl-3 col-md-5 col-sm-9" id="doc2" role="button" aria-pressed="false"
                    tabindex="0">
                    <h4 class="claim-info">How to backdate your claim</h4>
                    <p class="card-text">Learn how to backdate your claim along with Frequently Asked Questions related
                        to backdating.</p>
                    <span class="arrow">&#10230;</span>
                </div>
                <div class="custom-card col-xl-3 col-md-5 col-sm-9" id="doc3" role="button" aria-pressed="false"
                    tabindex="0">
